data.description:
Modern Elegance & Spacious Living: Updated Ranch Home in Pahrump with Mountain Views only 45 minutes from Las Vegas!
Discover contemporary rural living in this stunning 4000 Sq Ft. single-story ranch home in Pahrump, NV. Featuring 4 xtra large bedrooms, 4 baths, and a modern kitchen with marble countertops, Huge Center Island and stainless steel appliances. Main living space has open concept floorplan with living, family and dining rooms. Enjoy the convenience of a separate laundry room, ceiling fans, 2 of the 3 AC units are brand new, and a new water heater.
With an expansive 5-car garage, fully fenced backyard, well house, and water rights, this property offers both space and privacy. The circular driveway adds a touch of grandeur. Plus, the breathtaking mountain views provide a serene backdrop.
Embrace the elegance and natural beauty of this updated ranch home in Pahrump. It's a perfect retreat for those seeking modern luxury and a connection to nature. This LOAN is ASSUMABLE!!
